===Etymology===
From Latinised Greek [[gubernatio]] "management, government", from {{AGr.}} '''[[κυβερνισμός]]''', '''[[κυβέρνησις]]''' (''kybernismos'', ''kybernesis'') "steering, pilotage, guiding", from '''[[κυβερνάω]]''' (''kybernao'') "to steer, to drive, to guide, to act as a pilot" + ''[[-ment]]''.
